<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 15:12:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>乌克兰官员在北京敦促中国参加和平峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukrainian-official-beijing-urges-china-attend-peace-summit-2024-06-05/</link><description>乌克兰第一副外长周三访问中国，并敦促中国派代表团参加计划于本月在瑞士举行的乌克兰峰会，显然希望仍有可能说服中国参加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 14:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukrainian-official-beijing-urges-china-attend-peace-summit-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>帕劳总统称预计中国试图干预选举</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/palau-president-says-he-expects-china-try-meddle-election-2024-06-05/</link><description>太平洋岛国帕劳总统小苏兰杰·惠普斯在接受路透社采访时表示，预计中国将因承认台湾而试图干预今年晚些时候的全国选举。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/palau-president-says-he-expects-china-try-meddle-election-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>ASML 股价因 CFO Dassen 对订单的评论而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-rise-cfo-dassens-comments-orders-2024-06-05/</link><description>杰富瑞 (Jefferies) 分析师报告引用首席财务官罗杰·达森 (Roger Dassen) 的评论后，阿斯麦 (ASML) 股价周三上涨，该评论表明他对未来几个季度来自最大客户台积电 (TSMC) 的订单可能性持乐观态度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:30:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-rise-cfo-dassens-comments-orders-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>前新兴世界财政部长呼吁重新调整债务以支持气候支出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/former-emerging-world-finance-chiefs-call-debt-reworks-enable-climate-spending-2024-06-05/</link><description>根据周三发表的一封信，一群著名的前新兴市场金融主管正在敦促全球领导人将外部冲击和气候变化纳入债务可持续性计算中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/former-emerging-world-finance-chiefs-call-debt-reworks-enable-climate-spending-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年最大规模竞选即将来临，选举扰乱市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-election-2024-06-05/</link><description>墨西哥、南非和印度的选举结果都震动了货币和股市，这清楚地提醒人们，在占全球经济产出 60% 以上的国家和一半以上人口将投票的一年里，政治对市场来说仍然很重要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 12:14:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-election-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国中信将里昂证券离岸银行家的基本薪酬削减最多30%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-citic-cuts-clsa-offshore-banker-base-pay-by-up-30-sources-say-2024-06-05/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，由于交易量下降以及缩小与境内业务薪酬差距的压力，中信证券正在削减其离岸平台里昂证券 100 多名银行家的基本工资。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 11:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-citic-cuts-clsa-offshore-banker-base-pay-by-up-30-sources-say-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，中国最高的瀑布得到了管道的一点帮助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/highest-waterfall-china-gets-little-help-pipe-officials-say-2024-06-05/</link><description>中国河南省的风景公园经营者被迫承认，由于降雨不足，该国最高的瀑布得到了管道的帮助。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/highest-waterfall-china-gets-little-help-pipe-officials-say-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>印度钢铁部反对关键原材料进口限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-steel-ministry-against-import-curbs-key-raw-material-2024-06-05/</link><description>据知情人士和一份政府报告称，印度钢铁部反对限制低灰分冶金焦（一种炼钢原料）的进口，这可能对当地原材料生产商造成打击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:33:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-steel-ministry-against-import-curbs-key-raw-material-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：低迷买盘持续存在，加拿大将放松政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-05/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:10:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国热门新闻应用程序起源于中国并在人工智能的帮助下“写小说”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/top-news-app-us-has-chinese-origins-writes-fiction-with-help-ai-2024-06-05/</link><description>去年圣诞节前夕，NewsBreak（一款源自中国的免费应用程序，也是美国下载次数最多的新闻应用程序）发布了一篇关于小镇枪击事件的令人震惊的文章。其标题是“圣诞节悲剧袭击新泽西州布里奇顿，小镇枪支暴力不断上升”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:04:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/top-news-app-us-has-chinese-origins-writes-fiction-with-help-ai-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查发现中国5月份出口增长更快，提振增长前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-seen-rising-more-quickly-may-boosting-growth-prospects-2024-06-05/</link><description>由于海外需求的改善，中国的出口可能会在 5 月份连续第二个月快速增长，这让官员们在应对国内众多挑战以支撑不平衡的经济复苏时得到了一些安慰。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 09:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-seen-rising-more-quickly-may-boosting-growth-prospects-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国交易所考虑隐瞒量化基金的“某些”数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-exchanges-mull-withholding-certain-data-quant-funds-sources-say-2024-06-05/</link><description>两位消息人士称，上海和深圳证券交易所正在考虑暂停向计算机驱动的量化基金等机构提供某些增值市场数据，以加强对被认为导致市场波动的行业的审查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 09:32:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-exchanges-mull-withholding-certain-data-quant-funds-sources-say-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达CEO黄像流行歌星一样在台湾掀起“Jensanity”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/like-pop-star-nvidias-ceo-huang-stirs-up-jensanity-taiwan-2024-06-05/</link><description>自英伟达首席执行官黄仁勋抵达台湾一周半以来，他的一举一动都受到密切关注。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 08:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/like-pop-star-nvidias-ceo-huang-stirs-up-jensanity-taiwan-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>电动汽车推动沃尔沃汽车 5 月销量增长 13%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-may-sales-rise-13-2024-06-05/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车周三表示，得益于欧洲销量增长 27% 以及全电动 EX30 的强劲表现，沃尔沃汽车 5 月份销量增至 68,034 辆，同比增长 13%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 07:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-may-sales-rise-13-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在与巴勒斯坦对手法塔赫的会谈中展现了战后雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-signals-post-war-ambition-talks-with-palestinian-rival-fatah-2024-06-05/</link><description>本月巴勒斯坦派别哈马斯和法塔赫之间的深刻分歧将限制和解谈判的进展，但会议强调，在以色列加沙战争后，伊斯兰组织可能会保留影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 06:06:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-signals-post-war-ambition-talks-with-palestinian-rival-fatah-2024-06-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>